findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function _rLockBalanceOf() uses a loop to calculate total locked amount and may abort with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long locked list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges, including authorizing addresses, adding locked contracts, changing unlock timestamps, changing pair address, removing locks, and withdrawing contract BNBs and BEP20 tokens.
